---
title: Creamy Garlic Salmon Spaghetti with Nutmeg, Parmesan & Chives
description: This is our platonic ideal of a pasta meal—dreamy bowls of velvety spaghetti. You’ll simmer up a rich, creamy sauce tinged with a pinch of nutmeg for a subtle hint of warming spice (trust us, it’s the secret ingredient!), then add in al dente pasta and finish with juicy, garlicky seared chicken and a flourish of chopped chives and crushed red chili flakes. Work up that appetite, cause you’re in for a perfect bowl of luxurious pasta ready to be lovingly twirled and devoured.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/661d66433d20ae432f30b550-b4321f52.jpeg
